\":\"Target\"},{\"category\":\"With AI Batch Creation\",\"value\":100,\"group\":\"Target\"},{\"category\":\"With Full Automation\",\"value\":500,\"group\":\"Target\"}],\"width\":800,\"axisXTitle\":\"Production Method\",\"title\":\"Content Production Capacity Analysis\",\"group\":false,\"height\":500} View Recommended Pivot: Phase 1 (Month 1): 100 posts/day across 5 clusters = 20 posts per cluster Phase 2 (Month 2-3): Scale to 250 posts/day with automation Phase 3 (Month 4+): Hit 500 posts/day sustainable output STEP-BY-STEP IMPLEMENTATION GUIDE WEEK 1: Foundation Setup Day 1-2: Airtable Master Content Database Step\tAction\tExpected Input\tExpected Output 1.1\tSign up at Airtable.com\tEmail\tNew base created 1.2\tCreate base: \"Content Empire HQ\"\tClick \"+\" → \"Start from scratch\"\tBlank base 1.3\tRename first table to \"Content Master\"\tDouble-click table name\tTable renamed 1.4\tAdd fields (columns):\tClick \"+ \" repeatedly\t15 custom fields - Project Cluster (Single Select): SaaS, E-comm, Digital, Agency, Personal\t\tDropdown created - Content Type (Single Select): Social Post, Article, Video Script\t\tDropdown created - Platform (Multiple Select): LinkedIn, Twitter, Medium, Forbes\t\tMulti-select tags - Content Body (Long Text)\t\tText area - Headline (Single Line Text)\t\tText field - Publishing Date (Date)\t\tCalendar picker - Status (Single Select): Draft, Sched"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"[Content truncated — view full chat at source URL]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=f9342e2f-39c5-4c24-bb59-e5b08441ed2b","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=f9342e2f-39c5-4c24-bb59-e5b08441ed2b"}]}]}]
